<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"rscss-1-naming-components"}}>{`RSCSS-1: Naming Components`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`Components will be named with at least two words, separated by a dash. Examples of components:`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`A like button (.like-button)
A search form (.search-form)
